- email
- password_hash
- role

Missions
- id
- class
- subject
- topic

Questions
- id
- mission_id
- question
- options
- correct_answer

Progress
- id
- user_id
- mission_id
- completed
- score

Streaks
- user_id
- current_streak
- last_active_date

MentorRequests
- id
- student_id
- question_id
- status
- response

XP
- user_id
- total_xp

-----------------------------------
ADVANCED LOGIC
-----------------------------------

- Streak logic:
  - increase if daily login
  - reset if missed day

- At-risk detection:
  - low streak + low completion

- Mentor matching:
  - based on subject + availability

